Shenron (??; lit. &quot;Holy Dragon&quot; or &quot;God Dragon&quot;) is a magical dragon from the manga Dragon Ball, as well as the animes Dragon Ball, Dragon Ball Z, and Dragon Ball GT. In the English dub of Dragon Ball Z, he is mostly called the &quot;Eternal Dragon&quot; and, in the early Harmony Gold Dragon Ball English dub from the 1980s, he is known as the &quot;Dragon God.&quot;  
Model From: <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.models-resource.com/" >http://www.models-resource.com/</a>  
